reviewText: Came in great condition. The only thing that sucked was the video and audio messed up for about a minute in the middle of America Crude. The rest had no problem.

Got this for Christmas. It makes you laugh when you want to cry cause it turns all your bad feelings into good ones. You don't want to own this collection right here. On second thought, maybe you do want to own it.
None of these movies are real works of great merit. But some really bright spots that make it worth it
you have never paid for drugs. Not ONCE.
Can't beat getting 6 movies for the price. :)
